snippet: Sydney Wiese set the Pac-12 record for career 3-pointers and had 17 points and 11 rebounds to help No. 25 Oregon State beat Quinnipiac 75-60 in the semifinals of the Play4Kay Shootout on Tuesday night....
lead_paragraph: Sydney Wiese set the Pac-12 record for career 3-pointers and had 17 points and 11 rebounds to help No. 25 Oregon State beat Quinnipiac 75-60 in the semifinals of the Play4Kay Shootout on Tuesday night.

headline.main: Wiese Sets Pac-12 Record for Career 3s in Oregon State Win
headline.print_headline: Wiese Sets Pac-12 Record for Career 3s in Oregon State Win
